{"tid":1931321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【港產口罩】CareHK 口罩廠開幕 行會成員林健鋒牽頭料月底出貨每盒＄97.5","createTime":"2020-03-18T06:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T06:52:55.000Z","uid":51469,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fb7bb872db44154ec02a319bfd951b49304a851d","tid":1931321,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:10:13.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情持續，多家港產口罩廠經已成立，最新一家名為 CareHK，口罩廠於今天（17 日）正式開幕。CareHK 由匯愛香港有限公司經營，是由經民聯副主席、行政會員成員林健鋒牽頭成立。CareHK 口罩廠的廠房，正正是早前由本地農業初創綠芝園騰出來的用地【按此重溫報道】，位於大埔。今天林健鋒出席口罩廠開幕禮時，也帶同「匯愛」口罩樣板及包裝到場，供傳媒拍攝，並開放廠房供參觀。【按此睇 CareHK 口罩銷售 FAQ 懶人包】<br />\n<br />\n    CareHK 口罩廠於今天正式開幕<br />\n    口罩廠由行會成員林健鋒牽頭成立<br />\n    預計口罩會於 3 月底前出貨<br />\n<br />\n【其他報道】12 大連鎖商戶+小店最新口罩供貨免費派詳情 供貨情況即日（不斷更新） &lt;&lt;&lt;唔想錯過口罩開賣請 Bookmark<br />\n<br />\n在新聞發佈會上，CareHK 公佈一些口罩銷售詳情。發言人指出，口罩會符合 BFE 95% 以上的規格，成品將會送交 ASTM 作品質認證，有信心可達 ASTM Level 1 規格，預計 2 個星期後有結果。估計投資 1000 萬港元的 CareHK，直言會向政府申請「本地口罩生產資助計劃」，希望藉此保持口罩價格穩定。CareHK 首階段會設立 2 條生產線，首部口罩生產機已運抵，而本月內預料合計會有 3 - 4 條生產線，第 5 條生產線則預計於 4 月中投產，目標每天生產 50 萬片口罩，每月生產 1,500 萬片口罩。發佈會上，亦有口罩的初版包裝盒及口罩樣本供傳媒拍攝，可見 CareHK 會生產兩款尺寸的口罩，既有成人款，亦有小童款式，兩者同屬三層一次性口罩，沒有獨立包裝。<br />\n<br />\n【其他報道】藥房開訂日本口罩平售 $150盒/30個<br />\n<br />\n首批貨會捐出 20 萬個，口罩成品預計在 3 月底可出貨，產品暫定會在網上出售，成人款成價 $1.95 一個，以 50 個裝一盒而言，即 $97.5 一盒。CareHK 表示，未來一個月不會調整售價。匯愛 CareHK 口罩廠佔地約 8000 平方呎，達到 ISO 標準的無塵車間，官方指出，機器、生產線到包裝，都是香港設計，百份百 Made by HK。<br />\n<br />\n藍架,千祈唔好買呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7517e177ea264ba0f057104bd8992d07683bae","tid":1931321,"uid":324041,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"唔支持收成波!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864ae1b8bb8c85b66bd94068aa813f2a62a13e48","tid":1931321,"uid":54946,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:17:02.000Z","msg":"astm lv1"},{"pid":"43fb42e369f8584ecacea86cd0e2070fce55603a","tid":1931321,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9c7517e177ea264ba0f057104bd8992d07683bae","tid":1931321,"uid":324041,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"唔支持收成波!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ae443eeac9ae199d5e31d3f1f65d4739761333","tid":1931321,"uid":42582,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:18:53.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\nlevel 1都賣兩蚊一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a188f851db13055c76f288ada38bf74517e059e","tid":1931321,"uid":103914,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c7517e177ea264ba0f057104bd8992d07683bae","tid":1931321,"uid":324041,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"唔支持收成波!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:19:38.000Z","msg":"連仔幾時出左凸字版連登?"},{"pid":"6ca96061ecde6e1a99bf9b83e2e57d13eadbcd4a","tid":1931321,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"95ae443eeac9ae199d5e31d3f1f65d4739761333","tid":1931321,"uid":42582,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06: